OSX-SPECIFIC INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
-------------------------------------------

Building libdbi on OSX requires a little more typing compared to other
Unixes. This is what you need to do:

LIBTOOLIZE=glibtoolize ./autogen.sh
./configure CFLAGS="-I/sw/include" LDFLAGS="-L/sw/lib" 
make CFLAGS="-I/sw/include" LDFLAGS="-L/sw/lib" 
sudo make install


